                                        We are limited in providing details of Horseman’s Funds to investors who are not Professional Investors. In the UK you must be a Professional Client (as defined in the UK Financial Conduct Authority  (”FCA”) Rules) or for potential non-UK investors you otherwise are permitted to receive Fund details  pursuant to local private placement requirements.
